ONE person has died and 14 others sustained small to moderate injuries, after a taxi overturned multiple times in Umlazi KwaZulu Natal.According to Arrive Alive the Rescue Care Paramedics arrived at the scene and found &nbsp;a total bloodbath with several people injured. The person who died was thrown out of the taxi and suffered a number of &nbsp;injuries.&nbsp;14 people who were also in the taxi sustained minor to moderate injuries in the collision and were stabilized on the scene before being transported to nearby hospitals.The exact cause of the collision is unknown at this stage but SAPS &nbsp;is investigating the matter further.